</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span6 columns">
    
      <div class="well">
        <h2 class="page-header">Hire our ground</h2>    
        <h3>Quality cricket pitch, pavilion and professional tea for Â£200.</h3>
        <p>add pics and links etc</p>
